Main features:
    multithread;
    downloading via both http and ftp protocols;
    recursive downloading through both ftp and http protocol;
    queue of downloads;
    mask support;
    ftp and http proxy support;
    XWindow graphics userfriendly interface;
    supporting resuming files after connection's breaks (useful for far sites);
    logs for all downloads;
    common log;

Another features:
    more stable than other such programs for Linux :))
